  "about": [
    "Bluhm has donated generously to Northwestern University, where he studied law, most recently pledging $25 million to Northwestern Medicine in June 2018.",
    "A longtime Democratic donor, Bluhm donated $500,000 to Unite the Country, a super PAC supporting Joe Biden, in March 2020."
